        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks JS for abstract of orchid sterility paper from <hi rend="italic">Edinburgh Courant</hi>. His case of individual sterility will be of highest use to CD. Criticises JS’s writing. Points out weaknesses in the organisation of his argument and the use of inflated, imprecise language.</p> 
        </abstract>
